1
00:00:01,230 --> 00:00:02,630
Greetings everyone.

2
00:00:03,110 --> 00:00:13,130
Starting another project that's designed to ease searches for experimenters in free energy area.

3
00:00:14,150 --> 00:00:21,270
Block of scheme shown on this picture is power supply, universal for our experiments.

4
00:00:22,130 --> 00:00:25,450
Planned output voltage up to 1000 V.

5
00:00:25,450 --> 00:00:33,750
Also will run in this scheme new for me solution, this is work on opto-drivers.

6
00:00:36,010 --> 00:00:39,270
So why is such scheme needed?

7
00:00:39,470 --> 00:00:46,790
The thing is, can of course manage with bought power supplies.

8
00:00:46,790 --> 00:00:50,690
In particular, two I have.

9
00:00:51,330 --> 00:00:58,930
One of them low-voltage up to 30 V, other high-voltage up to 300 V.

10
00:00:59,390 --> 00:01:06,390
Seemingly voltage range normal and suitable, but there are some problems.

11
00:01:07,070 --> 00:01:11,690
First, these power supplies connect to mains.

12
00:01:11,690 --> 00:01:17,450
And connection to mains guarantees us connection with neutral.

13
00:01:17,950 --> 00:01:24,010
That is zero wire in lighting network inevitably tied to grounding.

14
00:01:24,530 --> 00:01:39,650
If we construct devices designed to get energy relative to earth, then with use of these power supplies we won't get anything, since we're already automatically tied to

15
00:01:39,650 --> 00:01:41,070
grounding through neutral.

16
00:01:41,690 --> 00:01:53,690
Seemingly could exclude connection with grounding, for example by turning on these power supplies through two transformers to isolate.

17
00:01:54,870 --> 00:01:58,990
But even in this case we also have connection.

18
00:01:59,070 --> 00:02:03,750
Anyway somehow it slips through and interferes with work.

19
00:02:04,610 --> 00:02:09,450
Could apply solution start power supplies through inverter.

20
00:02:09,450 --> 00:02:16,070
Yes, solution good and this solves main problem of earth connection.

21
00:02:16,650 --> 00:02:17,890
But there's one moment.

22
00:02:18,550 --> 00:02:27,530
All our experiments in most cases happen at pulse consumption from these power sources.

23
00:02:28,650 --> 00:02:38,790
And effects accompanying these experiments often so unpredictable that these power supplies behave absolutely inadequately.

24
00:02:39,450 --> 00:02:59,270
Generally, controllers start behaving chaotically, with this output voltage jumps, output current and besides, for example, of such power supply it starts giving operation in bursts mode.

25
00:02:59,890 --> 00:03:05,450
That is so strongly influence goes on it from these output wires.

26
00:03:05,450 --> 00:03:11,610
Tried putting filters here, this also doesn't save from this problem.

27
00:03:13,790 --> 00:03:16,310
Constant incorrect readings.

28
00:03:16,470 --> 00:03:32,850
And plus, when these blocks start working in pulse power supply mode, signal in form of bursts forms at output after key on control device.

29
00:03:32,850 --> 00:03:40,890
That is additional frequency modulation, and what naturally doesn't allow us to adequately tune system.

30
00:03:41,350 --> 00:03:47,910
So from these power blocks had to refuse due to their unsuitability.

31
00:03:48,770 --> 00:03:57,230
Such solutions very good for electronics tuning, they greatly help me.

32
00:03:57,230 --> 00:04:06,390
But unfortunately, for powering devices and for such experiments they're unsuitable.

33
00:04:06,950 --> 00:04:17,990
So was decided to develop this power supply that'll meet set tasks.

34
00:04:18,910 --> 00:04:23,630
In particular, same advice can give about oscilloscope use.

35
00:04:25,110 --> 00:04:33,450
Watching people's experiments, they connect oscilloscope to device and try to tune something.

36
00:04:34,010 --> 00:04:43,990
Forgetting that oscilloscope plugged into lighting network, common wire of oscilloscope inevitably tied to neutral.

37
00:04:43,990 --> 00:04:56,410
And turns out, even with power supply use we connect device and introduce same problem.

38
00:04:57,930 --> 00:05:06,460
In Nikola Tesla's times there was lighting network on direct current and there was no connection to neutral.

39
00:05:06,460 --> 00:05:14,800
Moreover, Nikola Tesla himself constructed devices that would allow him to work.

40
00:05:15,760 --> 00:05:21,700
Such as DC dynamo machines.

41
00:05:22,560 --> 00:05:34,220
Such dynamo machine gave autonomous power source and could be brought to rotation with help of external motor.

42
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:42,320
The thing is, all dynamo machines essentially are AC machines.

43
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:58,320
But if make dynamo machine with many contacts and do collector takeoff, can take from it potential at peak of AC wave.

44
00:05:58,320 --> 00:06:04,840
Thereby getting DC at output, which he was doing.

45
00:06:05,540 --> 00:06:08,560
But return to our scheme.

46
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:11,940
Examine it in more detail.

47
00:06:12,620 --> 00:06:21,320
First, power will be from battery, which solves our problem of connection with grounding.

48
00:06:21,320 --> 00:06:40,080
Next, I introduced relay element and diode so during our experiments with energetic effect inclusions in cheerful coil haze, not accidentally swap power wires.

49
00:06:41,400 --> 00:06:51,300
Such polarity reversal would inevitably lead to failure of keys and DC-DC converter that gives independent power.

50
00:06:53,380 --> 00:06:55,040
Solution simple.

51
00:06:55,440 --> 00:07:07,420
We have relay with normally-open contacts and there's winding that creates magnetic field, thereby attracting contact, and they close.

52
00:07:08,020 --> 00:07:18,320
If in correct direction install diode, can exclude wrong scheme inclusion.

53
00:07:18,320 --> 00:07:29,300
That is, when plus power applied to diode anode, current passes through it and naturally forming magnetic field, contacts attract.

54
00:07:29,840 --> 00:07:36,640
With reverse battery inclusion contact closure won't be.

55
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:47,100
Next introduced filter system, in capacities will be choke, well and already power applied to power keys.

56
00:07:47,980 --> 00:07:52,580
Decided to stop on full bridge scheme.

57
00:07:54,520 --> 00:08:03,440
Such scheme will allow qualitatively commutating primary winding and additionally introduce opto-isolations.

58
00:08:04,320 --> 00:08:07,900
Four opto-drivers controlling keys.

59
00:08:08,560 --> 00:08:13,340
Also introduced DC-DC converter with galvanic isolation.

60
00:08:13,340 --> 00:08:28,480
All this done so during our experiments no influence on PWM controller or drivers controlling keys, which could lead to incorrect system operation.

61
00:08:30,680 --> 00:08:42,340
In whole scheme quite simple, but there'll be nuances in its manufacture which I'll demonstrate along the way.

62
00:08:44,300 --> 00:08:53,680
For us will be introduced current feedback, thereby we can do current protection regulation.

63
00:08:53,780 --> 00:09:02,240
Very important parameter so if some shorting happened at output, system didn't fail.

64
00:09:03,860 --> 00:09:09,360
And this point can be regulated, thereby setting trigger threshold.

65
00:09:10,320 --> 00:09:19,040
Also will be introduced pulse duration regulation, which ultimately will be responsible for output voltage.

66
00:09:19,100 --> 00:09:32,360
That is on each transformer lead we'll have voltage regulation from zero to maximum that allows turn count of this transformer.

67
00:09:33,160 --> 00:09:45,140
At that transformer will be made on ferrite ring and secondary winding will have taps.

68
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:58,200
Here I schematically marked taps that'll go to switch and between taps can switch, thereby regulating maximum output voltage.

69
00:09:59,200 --> 00:10:08,200
Voltage feedback can't be introduced here due to scheme being very bulky.

70
00:10:08,520 --> 00:10:18,900
Will have to use same switch that'll change resistor circuits that'll set feedback trigger point.

71
00:10:18,900 --> 00:10:23,820
But in PWM controller I'll introduce this system.

72
00:10:24,700 --> 00:10:38,800
Say, if we need to hold on some lead constant voltage, we just take from here potential of this voltage, create resistor divider and feed back.

73
00:10:39,240 --> 00:10:45,020
Say, we have tested scheme of some transistor and we precisely know its parameters.

74
00:10:45,020 --> 00:10:46,940
This can be done.

75
00:10:47,220 --> 00:10:54,020
And so, main switching of voltage potential will be done with switch help.

76
00:10:55,060 --> 00:11:04,800
And output voltage will be calculated by Ohm's law on load, where current multiplied by load resistance.

77
00:11:06,120 --> 00:11:21,240
But since for us power will be pulse, taken from output of this converter, this formula will be incorrect a little, but this quite suits us.

78
00:11:23,880 --> 00:11:33,140
Before moving to making this scheme, need to first buy all parts.

79
00:11:33,140 --> 00:11:44,560
So far at my place found such switch that perfectly suits us from Soviet equipment.

80
00:11:44,860 --> 00:11:52,060
It has ceramic contact pad and quite powerful terminal output.

81
00:11:52,060 --> 00:12:11,700
Here I drew where additional work on terminals is needed, because now if we switch, visible that switch due to contact pad width temporarily closes contact.

82
00:12:11,840 --> 00:12:16,700
This need to get rid of and switch will be fully suitable.

83
00:12:16,700 --> 00:12:34,080
Switch has 12 leads in circle, one of them common, from it supply voltage will be taken, and this petal does commutation.

84
00:12:35,800 --> 00:12:41,920
In this case I drew on 12 leads, but at my place found 11-lead switch.

85
00:12:42,920 --> 00:12:45,780
Not critical, quite suits us.

86
00:12:46,580 --> 00:12:52,940
Can pick any here, who'll like, for output rating.

87
00:12:53,800 --> 00:13:05,030
Of details that set common system dimensions, already have ready DC-DC converter.

88
00:13:06,030 --> 00:13:14,370
Video on its tuning and making can look in previous video clip on my channel.

89
00:13:15,550 --> 00:13:21,510
Specifically made for purpose of installation in this universal power supply.

90
00:13:22,190 --> 00:13:23,770
It'll be located here.

91
00:13:25,090 --> 00:13:28,790
For all other parts I go to store.

92
00:13:29,790 --> 00:13:35,230
After this when I buy, move to manufacture.

93
00:13:35,870 --> 00:13:43,250
And at same time count how such universal power supply works out by price of radio parts.

94
00:13:45,030 --> 00:13:47,150
Thanks to all who watched.

95
00:13:47,690 --> 00:13:49,210
Awaiting next release.
